00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,320
You still have a chance. It's okay.

267
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:11,720
[Huang Jing crying]

268
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:20,680
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE

269
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:25,320
[player 1] Hurry up! We will be late!

270
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,160
Why haven't they come?

271
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,360
They said they are on the way.

272
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,960
If they are late, they'll lose by default.

273
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:40,600
-Why are we grouped with them again?
-That's right.

274
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:42,880
-We can't win.
-How is it? Who is grouped with us?

275
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:44,880
-Why are you so late?
-It is them again.

276
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,400
[player 2] That's right.

277
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,440
[inhales sharply]

278
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:52,360
If people from Yu Feng
don't come here by the set time,

279
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,720
they will lose by default.

280
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,360
That means...

281
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:58,240
we will qualify into the next round.

282
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,960
[chuckling]

283
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:02,120
Yes, it is winning without competition.

284
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:03,280
MA LINTAO
NO. 3 HIGH SCHOOL

285
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,760
Why is that always the case
when you are here with us?

286
00:17:04,839 --> 00:17:06,800
I want to play occasionally.

287
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,800
I'm so bored.

288
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:10,839
Your luck makes the match so boring.

289
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,400
-That's right.
-I am lucky.

290
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,480
[Qianshi] I am really lucky.

291
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:20,440
Eh? Where are they?

292
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:23,880
TAN YITAI
TEAM MEMBER OF NO. 3 HIGH SCHOOL

293
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:26,960
He was here just now.

294
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,880
There is so much trash.

295
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,040
[Jiuxin] What are you doing?

296
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,120
[gasps]

297
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,880
Sorry, Jiuxin.

298
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:44,480
[sighs]
Jiuxin, where have you been?

299
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:45,800
Something serious has happened.

300
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,320
Yu Feng has only three players.

301
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:49,360
But the assembly time is almost up.

302
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:51,920
If they can't make it on time,
they will lose by default.

303
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:55,280
You should go to the match quickly
or you'll lose by default as well.

304
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:59,800
I hate it when someone orders me.

305
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:04,240
Jiuxin, where are you going?

306
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:07,320
Don't run away again.

307
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:10,360
This newcomer doesn't seem to be afraid
of Ya Jiuxin at all.

308
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:11,960
[sighs]

309
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:16,040
Since Ya Jiuxin came,
we have to sneak to practice tennis.

310
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,200
NAN JIANZHI
NO. 3 HIGH SCHOOL

311
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:20,080
I think it is great.
He is a brilliant player.

312
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:25,360
Let me check. I'll go see
if they aren't at the checkpoint yet.

313
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:30,520
Where have you been?
Be quick. Time is running out.

314
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,720
Eh.

315
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:35,080
What's wrong with your hand?

316
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:37,200
Nothing. Let's go to the assembly.

317
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,960
What happened?

318
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:50,360
We just had a traffic accident.

319
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,600
What? Is it serious?

320
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,280
[Ziping] Do you want to hide

321
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:56,120
such an important matter?

322
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,640
Do you want to play the match
with injuries?

323
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:01,760
[tense music]

324
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:12,640
Captain, I can still play.

325
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:16,040
Captain, don't blame them for this.

326
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:17,760
They don't want to let you down.

327
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:28,280
They are thinking about going to the match
in such terrible condition.

328
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:31,200
You are all an essential part of the team.

329
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:33,600
Who will take responsibility
if any of you are hurt?

330
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,600
Who will win the championship?

331
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:40,760
We don't take it easy during our matches,

332
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,240
we do our best instead, right?

333
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,320
Captain.

334
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:45,360
-Captain.
-Captain.

335
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,440
-Sorry.
-Sorry.

336
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,480
Sorry.

337
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:51,560
Let's go to the hospital.

338
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,200
[Jiuxin] What a shame.

339
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,600
[tense music]

340
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:11,040
You can be so hot-blooded
when it comes to tennis.

341
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,560
[scoffs]

342
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,000
It is so disgusting.

343
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:16,960
Weiming.

344
00:20:18,080 --> 00:20:19,280
What?

345
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:21,320
Are you afraid?

346
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,960
Don't fall for his trap.

347
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:26,480
If we fight here,
we will lose the right to compete.

348
00:20:27,080 --> 00:20:27,920
[scoffs]

349
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:30,600
Let's go.

350
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:46,440
[Siyang] Captain Xu, are you okay?

351
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:50,080
Although we gave up the match,

352
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:53,000
I still remember our deal.
We will make it happen.

353
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:56,520
Okay, see you on the court again.

354
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,120
Mmm.

355
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,920
Yu Qing.

356
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:09,040
Don't you give up like them.

357
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:17,360
It is him again.

358
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:21,280
This time, we must win.

359
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:27,200
-The Yu Feng Tennis Team has given up.
-Really?

360
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:28,560
-Huh?
-Yes.

361
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:30,520
Their members came,
but they gave up the match?

362
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,760
Yes.

363
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:34,080
But all their team members gave up.

364
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,400
[scoffs]

365
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,720
I think you're terrifying.

366
00:21:38,560 --> 00:21:39,600
-[sighs]
-Mmm.

367
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,160
[Qianshi] We should keep a low profile.

368
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:43,600
-Yes.
-Lucky!

369
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,920
We are sure to win.

370
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:46,600
[Jingtian] Defeat Yu Qing...

371
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:49,120
and have Ying Cai build a new era.

372
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,600
We were humiliated that day.

373
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,840
We are not the same as we used to be.

374
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:56,200
[Dahai] Thirty players were defeated
by one person.

375
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:58,280
We will never forget something like that.

376
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,240
We should thank him.

377
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:04,240
Hmm. Yu Qing is coming.

378
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:05,440
[all gasp]

379
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:16,400
[Jingtian] Why are you hiding here?

380
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:18,280
-And there--
-[Ye] Shut up!

381
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:23,840
That is the captain of Yu Qing, right?

382
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,040
He is Mu Siyang.

383
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:29,160
[Jingtian] I heard that the Chinese
tennis team is interested in him.

384
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,520
It seems we are not on the same level.

385
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:33,800
We should aim for someone else.

386
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,360
[Dahai] Chi Dayong and Tang Jiale,

387
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:40,200
the Golden Partners of Yu Qing.

388
00:22:40,280 --> 00:22:43,880
They got good results in the National
Senior High Doubles Competition last year.

389
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,720
Is that true?

390
00:22:45,840 --> 00:22:48,560
[Ye] That means we have to give up
on the first two matches.

391
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:50,560
But it doesn't matter,

392
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:53,120
we only have to win three matches
out of five.

393
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:58,240
[Jingtian] Look at these two,
one of them is Zhang Baiyang.

394
00:22:58,320 --> 00:23:01,080
He likes to play tricks
on exhausted opponents.

395
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:03,680
And he is fierce.

396
00:23:03,760 --> 00:23:06,360
The one beside him looks more gentle.

397
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,680
[Dahai] He is also from Grade 11.
He is Qiao Chen.

398
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:11,760
I hear that he used
his best smash technique

399
00:23:11,840 --> 00:23:14,160
in his last competition with Guozi.

400
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:15,560
What?

401
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,240
[Ye gasps]

402
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:24,320
[Dahai] And that's He Xinglong,
he looks like someone easy to beat,

403
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:27,760
but as long as he holds a racket,
he is extremely aggressive.

404
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:30,920
He can serve balls with a speed
of 200 kilometers per hour.

405
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:33,240
He broke countless rackets.

406
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:35,440
And Zhuo Zhi,

407
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,880
known to be the second strongest player
in Yu Qing.

408
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:41,800
If all this is true,
then we have little hope of winning.

409
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,400
Nothing is impossible.

410
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:48,440
I heard that Yu Qing recruited students
from Grade 10 for unknown reasons.

411
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,400
And he is short.

412
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:51,480
[scoffs]

413
00:23:52,080 --> 00:23:53,200
Grade 10?

414
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,760
Then we are sure to defeat him.

415
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,680
He is no match for us.

416
00:23:57,920 --> 00:24:00,520
[Ye] I will deal with the boy
from Grade 10.

417
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:05,440
[playful music]

418
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:09,560
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

419
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:12,760
Hello.

420
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:15,000
Why are you here?

421
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,320
-It is him.
-It is him.

422
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,360
It is him.

423
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,680
You have to admit defeat,

424
00:24:19,760 --> 00:24:22,240
or else I won't return the tennis balls
I won from you last time.

425
00:24:34,760 --> 00:24:36,760
[playful music]

426
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:40,680
Eh?

427
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:41,920
Dachi,

428
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:46,120
why do the team members
of Ying Cai look so serious?

429
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:50,520
We can't treat the match lightly,
depending on their momentum.

430
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:56,520
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE
YING CAI VERSUS YU QING

431
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:58,360
[umpire 1] Both sides, shake hands.

432
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:05,400
[all groaning]

433
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,800
[Jingtian] Umpire, we can't play anymore.
We give up.

434
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,040
What's wrong?

435
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:14,480
[umpire 1] Ying Cai High School gives up.
Yu Qing qualifies into the next round.

436
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:17,440
Huh? We have won?

437
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:23,840
You pretend to be ill and give up
because you fear losing to Yu Qing.

438
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,440
Who are you talking to?

439
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,160
Qiao Chen.

440
00:25:27,320 --> 00:25:30,000
Ya Jiuxin, you went too far.

441
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:33,600
You should celebrate
for getting such a big advantage.

442
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:35,760
Oh, I remember.

443
00:25:36,040 --> 00:25:38,000
You are going to compete with us
in the next round.

444
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:41,200
You will not be happy then
because you will lose for sure.

445
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:44,120
Qiao Chen, come back.
Don't get into trouble.

446
00:25:46,320 --> 00:25:47,240
[sighs]

447
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:49,800
[Lu Xia] Hey,

448
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:52,320
you said we would meet in the competition.

449
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:55,800
Don't be so frightened as to give up now.

450
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:56,960
Okay.

451
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:00,640
I will deal with you in the competition.

452
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:07,200
You are far from being a match for me.

453
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,120
YU QING

454
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,440
[Coach Qi] The next competition

455
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:19,400
will be between us and No.3 High School
for the municipal championship.

456
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,560
It means a lot.

457
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:22,920
I hope everyone
can pay more attention to it.

458
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,800
Sorry, I am late.

459
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,400
I had something to deal with at home.

460
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,480
Sit down.

461
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,760
Since everyone is here,

462
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:43,560
I will share information
on No.3 High School.

463
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:52,200
I summarized it into three points.

464
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:55,760
-Number 3 refers to--
-Because they are No.3 High School.

465
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,040
[inhales sharply]

466
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,400
[sighs]

467
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,400
[soft chuckle]

468
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:07,360
Number 3 refers to their third
singles player, Qianshi, the captain.

469
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,480
He is a legendary player.

470
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:12,960
He has good luck.
People call him Lucky Qianshi.

471
00:27:13,320 --> 00:27:14,280
[Zhuo Zhi] I know him.

472
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:17,480
He was selected in the Teenager Trial
when he was in junior high.

473
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:18,960
He's an excellent player.

474
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:22,480
Number 2 refers to their doubles.

475
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:25,480
They even defeated our Golden Partners
last year.

476
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,800
You can imagine how good they are.

477
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:31,400
But it won't be the same this year.
Right, Dachi?

478
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:32,360
Mm-hmm.

479
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:34,520
Number 1 means

480
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:38,160
we can still win
even if we lose the doubles match

481
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:41,080
because No.3 High School
doesn't have a strong singles player.

482
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,520
But because Ya Jiuxin joined the team,

483
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:45,680
the advantage we had last year

484
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:48,600
has become a huge challenge
that we have to overcome this year.

485
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:58,200
If we count Yu Qing's advantages,

486
00:27:58,760 --> 00:28:00,280
we'll have more than theirs.

487
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,440
What is it?

488
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:04,920
-It's 666 for awesome--
-Sit down right now.

489
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:07,120
[Qiao Chen clears throat]

490
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:12,200
Now, I will announce the competitors' list
I reported to the committee.

491
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,680
The second doubles,

492
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:17,040
He Xinglong and Zhuo Zhi.

493
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,320
The first doubles,

494
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:21,920
Chi Dayong and Tang Jiale.

495
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:24,800
The third singles, Qiao Chen...

496
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:25,920
Yes!

497
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:28,000
Qiao Chen, are you okay with it?

498
00:28:28,080 --> 00:28:31,320
Of course not. I am hardworking.

499
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:33,560
[Qiao Chen]
I am the enemy of Lucky Qianshi.

500
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,400
Can you be silent for a while?

501
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,520
[chuckles]

502
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:41,000
The second singles
who will compete with Ya Jiuxin is...

503
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:42,960
Lu Xia.

504
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:45,080
I won't lose the match.

505
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,440
I will go to training.

506
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:52,320
Whoa! It is so rare for Lu Xia
to be so active.

507
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:54,400
It seems we can watch a great show
this time.

508
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:58,440
The first singles still goes to Siyang.

509
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,440
Okay. Everyone, please go to training.

510
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,200
-Be quick!
-[Tang Jiale] Let's go.

511
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:13,840
Coach.

512
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:19,120
Ya Jiuxin doesn't play in a normal way.

513
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,320
He often hurts his opponents
in competitions.

514
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:23,840
I am concerned that Lu Xia
won't be able to deal with him.

515
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,440
[exhales sharply]
That depends.

516
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,520
[thwacks]

517
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,680
[sighs deeply]

518
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,280
[sizzling]

519
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:02,560
Maybe another cold dish?

520
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,000
There should be enough nourishment.

521
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:20,120
XINGLONG

522
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,200
Then I'll see you on the court.

523
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,840
[Jiuxin] I hope you won't
get hurt anymore.

524
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:42,480
Dad.

525
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:45,720
You are home early today.
Don't you have training?

526
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:48,040
I just wanted to come earlier to help you.

527
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:51,160
You don't have to worry about it.
Just play tennis well.

528
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:53,440
I know.

529
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:55,720
I will go to Mr. Lin's
to buy some soy sauce.

530
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:56,760
I will be right back.

531
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:01,640
Be careful when riding the bike.

532
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,440
Go away.

533
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,840
Don't interrupt my sleep.

534
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,600
[He Xinglong] Tomorrow.

535
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:48,080
Don't hurt my friend.

536
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,400
[scoffs]

537
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,240
You should know it already.

538
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:55,160
I will always keep my promises.

539
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:59,000
Plus, I feel disgusted

540
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:01,880
to see you love and care
for each other so much.

541
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,640
[somber music]

542
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:09,160
[exhales sharply]

543
00:32:10,560 --> 00:32:11,440
[groans]

544
00:32:14,800 --> 00:32:19,560
Did those losers ask you to beg?

545
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:22,640
No. It is my own decision.

546
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:25,800
Go and tell your crap friends,

547
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,440
the one with a cap...

548
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:32,400
will surely lose tomorrow.

549
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:36,200
Ya Jiuxin, what do you want to do?

550
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:45,160
I will make him stop playing tennis.

551
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:47,720
[gasps]
You are not serious, are you?

552
00:32:47,800 --> 00:32:48,640
[exhales sharply]

553
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,360
[scoffs]

554
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:54,280
What do you think?

555
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,520
Stop caring for others...

556
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:03,640
and take care of your roast geese.

557
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:06,720
[scoffs]
Don't get it overcooked.

558
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:22,040
[thwacking]

559
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:25,800
Great. That guy is practicing.

560
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:28,440
I can finally watch the show
without interruption.

561
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,880
[static]

562
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,880
[comical music]

563
00:33:47,080 --> 00:33:49,320
[mumbles]

564
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:52,160
I...

565
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:55,120
Lu Xia, stop playing!

566
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,480
Stop...

567
00:33:58,880 --> 00:33:59,880
Oh!

568
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:01,720
I'm screwed!

569
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,520
I'm screwed!

570
00:34:09,120 --> 00:34:10,639
[Xiangqian sighs]

571
00:34:19,719 --> 00:34:20,920
What's wrong with the TV?

572
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,760
You hit it too hard.

573
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,480
Are you satisfied?

574
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,800
Then I will go to bed.

575
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:31,719
Wait.

576
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:35,000
There will be a match tomorrow.
How about your preparations?

577
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:37,480
No problem.

578
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:44,360
The PIN number is your birthday.

579
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:46,320
[gasps]
A credit card?

580
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:48,400
Haven't you been hurt before?

581
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:50,120
If you get hurt in the match again...

582
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,520
you can use it.

583
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:01,600
[Lu Xia] A medical insurance card.

584
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:03,440
I don't need it.

585
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:05,520
[Xiangqian] That would be the best.

586
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:14,080
[birds chirping]

587
00:35:19,080 --> 00:35:19,920
[sighs]

588
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:23,640
Shasha, you are sure to
be accepted into the internship.

589
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:28,640
[light music]

590
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,760
Where is the court?

591
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:40,920
[Peng and Ying panting]

592
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,280
[Peng and Ying] Xiao Sha.

593
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,960
-Are you lost again?
-It's that way.

594
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:46,640
Are you here to pick me up?

595
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:48,120
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

596
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:53,760
[woman 1] Are you ready, Yu Qing?

597
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,520
The match is about to begin

598
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:58,360
Sorry, ma'am,
but a team member went to the toilet.

599
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,960
-He will be here right away.
-What is taking him so long?

600
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:05,920
One more minute.

601
00:36:07,240 --> 00:36:08,200
[Dayong] It is awful.

602
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:13,920
-[Mu] I am here.
-[Dayong] He is here, ma'am.

603
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:19,120
Did you deliberately come here
at the last moment?

604
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:21,000
[Lu Xia] Sorry, I am late.

605
00:36:27,240 --> 00:36:29,200
[gasps]
Lu Xia, you are here.

606
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:32,880
There are two Lu Xias.

607
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:34,640
There is a real and a fake Lu Xia?

608
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:38,880
I know Lu Xia will be late. So...

609
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:42,960
Lu Xia, if you are late again next time...

610
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:47,040
Lu Xia, is it because you helped others
on the way again?

611
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,160
I sent a pregnant woman to the hospital.

612
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:52,760
Anyway, I managed to be here
at the last minute.

613
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:56,240
Captain, don't tell me you suddenly
want to play again.

614
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,480
[Lu Xia] I really didn't mean to be late.

615
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:03,320
Okay, since you're here,
you can now check-in.

616
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,600
Chi Dayong and Tang Jiale.

617
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:06,920
Zhuo Zhi and He Xinglong.

618
00:37:07,080 --> 00:37:10,080
This time, the doubles
of No.3 High School are very strong.

619
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:12,200
[Siyang] Don't be stressed.

620
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:13,560
Do your best.

621
00:37:13,640 --> 00:37:16,200
Please lose a game or two
so I can have a chance of playing.

622
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,480
[inhales sharply]

623
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:25,040
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE

624
00:37:25,120 --> 00:37:26,440
[cheering]

625
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:28,320
Now, Yu Qing's second doubles players.

626
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:30,680
[umpire 2] Zhuo Zhi and He Xinglong,
please enter the court.

627
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:35,480
[tense music]

628
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,120
[Zhuo Zhi] Don't worry.

629
00:37:49,200 --> 00:37:50,480
It is okay. Just do your best.

630
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:53,760
Oh. I will.

631
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:58,560
[tense music]

632
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:09,720
I heard that Yu Qing has a main player
from Grade 10.

633
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,320
I must conduct a survey on it.

634
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,720
Why is my hairband always falling?

635
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:15,560
[gasps]

636
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,840
Why are you so careless?

637
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:22,720
-I am so sorry.
-Never mind.

638
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:25,440
Eh?

639
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:28,200
Are you from Yu Qing?

640
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:33,160
Are you here to cheer
for the player named Lu Xia

641
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:35,080
who is from Grade 10?

642
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,400
Oh.

643
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,480
[Yitai] He is brilliant.

644
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:43,400
I am curious about
how he became a main player.

645
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:46,280
Oh. I almost forgot.

646
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:49,240
Hey, I have some questions to ask you.

647
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,240
What is Lu Xia's zodiac sign?

648
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,760
I don't know.

649
00:38:54,520 --> 00:38:55,720
What about his blood type?

650
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,080
I don't know.

651
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:02,840
I have another important question.
How tall is Lu Xia?

652
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:05,480
[playful music]

653
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,080
He's 180cm tall.

654
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,080
Really?

655
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,200
He's really 178cm.

656
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:18,520
Give me the real data.

657
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:22,640
-He's 168cm.
-Huh?

658
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,440
He is so short.

659
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:27,160
Almost as short as me.

660
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:31,600
I thought he was as tall as Ya Jiuxin.
[chuckling]

661
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,200
Okay.

662
00:39:36,520 --> 00:39:38,480
Thank you so much.

663
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:40,480
I didn't expect you to know him so well.

664
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,440
The freshman
who became a regular in Yu Qing

665
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:45,840
turned out to be a shorty.
[chuckling]

666
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,240
Thank you.

667
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,960
Are you on the tennis team?

668
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:52,520
Yes.

669
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:56,720
But I am just in charge of logistics
because I am too short.

670
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:01,640
[Tang Jiale]
Lu Xia, we should go to the court now.

671
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:03,120
I must go now.

672
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:08,520
Lu Xia?

673
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:20,000
Height is not the only thing that matters
when playing tennis.

674
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:27,480
MA YIDUO, DU MIXIN
VERSUS ZHUO ZHI, HE XINGLONG

675
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,320
[umpire 2] Score!

676
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:36,760
It's 2-5.

677
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,360
No.3 High School takes the lead.

678
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:41,040
[panting]

679
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,000
It doesn't matter.

680
00:40:47,640 --> 00:40:48,600
Oh.

681
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:51,880
[students sighing]

682
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:55,160
I didn't expect Zhuo Zhi and Xinglong
would be overwhelmed like this.

683
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:57,080
I don't know why,

684
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:59,320
but they haven't found a way
to break through.

685
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:02,920
Xinglong seems to be too defensive.

686
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:05,960
[Sha] No.3 High School
is good at attacking,

687
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:07,960
