joined their team.

688
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:09,720
They have a stronger offensive style now.

689
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:12,600
Yes. I saw Ya Jiuxin the other day.

690
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:14,360
He is not easy to deal with.

691
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,760
Huang Jing and the other two
competed with him.

692
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:18,760
But they couldn't even receive his ball.

693
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:25,080
Look, Jiuxin, Lu Xia is as short as me.

694
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:27,280
But he is already a main player.

695
00:41:30,160 --> 00:41:32,160
[tense music]

